# Metadata schema

DataCite and DCMI both provide well-established metadata scheme.

DataCite provides the schema definition in XSD format at https://schema.datacite.org/meta/kernel-4.4/metadata.xsd.

For visualization, use [xsdvi](https://sourceforge.net/projects/xsdvi/) as follows:

```
mkdir -p vis
cd vis
curl https://schema.datacite.org/meta/kernel-4.4/metadata.xsd > datacite_metadata_schema_v4.4.xsd
java -jar /path/to/xsdvi/dist/lib/xsdvi.jar datacite_metadata_schema_v4.4.xsd
```

The generated `datacite_metadata_schema_v4.4.svg` can be explored with a browser.
